text: Associação Boquinhense de Desportos, commonly known as Boquinhense, is a Brazilian football club based in Boquim, Sergipe state. ==History== The club was founded on October 11, 1965. ==Stadium== Associação Boquinhense de Desportos play their home games at Estádio Temístocles Carvalho, nicknamed Temistão. The stadium has a maximum capacity of 3,000 people. ==References== Category:Association football clubs established in 1965 Category:Football clubs in Sergipe Category:1965 establishments in Brazil
title: Associação Boquinhense de Desportos
